*% ========== 5.4 Installable Options, and Constraints ======================================

*OpenGroup: InstallableOptions

*OpenUI *InstalledMemory: PickOne
*DefaultInstalledMemory: 32Meg
*InstalledMemory  32Meg: ""
*?InstalledMemory: "currentsystemparams /RamSize get 1048576 div cvi 10 string cvs print (Meg)="
*CloseUI: *InstalledMemory

*% Other installable options go here

*CloseGroup: InstallableOptions

*% ========== 5.5 Basic Device Capabilities =================================================

*ColorDevice: True
*DefaultColorSpace: CMYK
*FileSystem: True
*?FileSystem: "
false
(*) {
	/DevDict exch currentdevparams def
	DevDict /Writeable known {DevDict /Writeable get} {false} ifelse
	DevDict /Mounted   known {DevDict /Mounted   get} {false} ifelse
	DevDict /HasNames  known {DevDict /HasNames  get} {false} ifelse
	and and {pop true} if
} 128 string /IODevice resourceforall
{(True)} {(False)} ifelse ="
*End
*LanguageLevel: "3"
*Throughput: "120"
*TTRasterizer: Type42
*?TTRasterizer: "(Type42) ="

*% ========== 5.6 System Management =========================================================

*% *PatchFile  would go here for bugs found subsequent to release of this PPD
*% *?PatchFile would go here for bugs found subsequent to release of this PPD
*% *JobPatchFile would go here for bugs found subsequent to release of this PPD
*FreeVM: "30135136"
*FCacheSize 32Meg: 204800
*VMOption 32Meg/Standard: "30135136"

*Reset: "
 count 0 eq
 { false } { true exch startjob } ifelse
 not {
    (WARNING: Cannot reset printer.) =
    (Missing or invalid password.) =
    (Please contact the author of this software.) = flush quit
    } if
 systemdict /quit get exec
 (WARNING : Printer Reset Failed.) = flush
"
*End

*Password: "0"

*ExitServer: "
count 1 ge {true exch startjob} {false} ifelse
not {
   (ERROR: *ExitServer cannot start unencapsulated job.) =
   (       Password is probably invalid.) =
} if"
*End

*SuggestedJobTimeout: "0"
*SuggestedWaitTimeout: "300"
*PrintPSErrors: True
*% *DeviceAdjustMatrix should not be used for new PPDs with new products

*% ========== 5.7 Emulations and Protocols ==================================================

*% 5.8 ========== Features Accessible Only Through Job Control Language =====================

*% ========== 5.9 Resolution and Appearance Control =========================================
*OpenUI *Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 19.0 AnySetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 300x300dpi
*Resolution 300x300dpi: ""
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*OpenUI *NTLResolution/Calidad de la imagen: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20.0 AnySetup *NTLResolution
*DefaultNTLResolution: 300x300dpi
*NTLResolution 300x300dpi/Estßndar (300 x 300 dpi): "
%PPD_VERSION=4.02 2009.01.21
%PPD_Resolution=300x300
%PPD_GammaUse=0
"
*End
*NTLResolution 300x600dpi/Alta definici¾n (300 x 600 dpi): "
%PPD_VERSION=4.02 2009.01.21
%PPD_Resolution=300x600
%PPD_GammaUse=0
"
*End
*?NTLResolution: "
  save
    currentpagedevice /HWResolution get 0 get
    cvi (   ) cvs print (dpi) = flush
  restore
"
*End
*CloseUI: *NTLResolution

*% ========== 5.10 Gray Levels and Halftoning ===============================================

*%ContoneOnly: True
*ScreenAngle: "45"
*ScreenFreq: "80"
*DefaultScreenProc: Dot
*ScreenProc Dot: "{abs exch abs 2 copy add 1 le {dup mul exch dup mul add 1 exch sub}
{1 sub dup mul exch 1 sub dup mul add 1 sub} ifelse}
bind"
*End

*DefaultTransfer: Null

*% ========== 5.11 Color Adjustment =========================================================

*OpenUI *ColorModel/Modo color: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 21.0 AnySetup *ColorModel
*DefaultColorModel: CMYK
*ColorModel CMYK/Color: "%PPD_ColorModel=1"
*ColorModel Gray/Monocromo: "%PPD_ColorModel=0"
*?ColorModel: "
  save
    currentpagedevice /ProcessColorModel get
    dup /DeviceCMYK eq
      { pop (CMYK) }
      { /DeviceGray eq
        { (Gray) }
        { (CMYK) }
      ifelse }
    ifelse
    = flush
  restore
"
*End
*CloseUI: *ColorModel

*ColorRenderDict DefaultColorRendering: "/DefaultColorRendering /ColorRendering findresource setcolorrendering"
*ColorRenderDict AppleMonitor: "/AppleMonitor /ColorRendering findresource setcolorrendering"
*ColorRenderDict CRDAbsolute: "/CRDAbsolute /ColorRendering findresource setcolorrendering"
*ColorRenderDict CRDPerceptual: "/CRDPerceptual /ColorRendering findresource setcolorrendering"
*ColorRenderDict CRDRelative: "/CRDRelative /ColorRendering findresource setcolorrendering"
*ColorRenderDict CRDSaturation: "/CRDSaturation /ColorRendering findresource setcolorrendering"

*RenderingIntent: DefaultColorRendering

*% ========== 5.14 Media Selection ==========================================================

*OpenUI *InputSlot/Bandeja de alimentaci¾n de papel: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 22.0 AnySetup *InputSlot
*DefaultInputSlot: Tray1
*InputSlot Slot/Selecci¾n automßtica de la bandeja: "%PPD_InputSlot=0"
*InputSlot Tray1/Bandeja de Alimentaci¾n 1: "%PPD_InputSlot=3"
*InputSlot Tray2/Bandeja de Alimentaci¾n 2: "%PPD_InputSlot=4"
*InputSlot ManualFeed/Bandeja de Alimentaci¾n Estßndar: "%PPD_InputSlot=2"
*?InputSlot: "currentpagedevice /ManualFeed get {(ManualFeed)} {
    (TraySelect ?) 16 string /CPSI /ProcSet findresource
    /externalcommand get exec pop
     dup (0) eq { pop (Slot) } {
      dup (3) eq { pop (Tray1) } {
       dup (4) eq { pop (Tray2) } {
        dup (2) eq { pop (ManualFeed) } {
         pop (Slot)
        } ifelse
       } ifelse
      } ifelse
     } ifelse
  } ifelse ="
*End
*CloseUI: *InputSlot

*OpenUI *MediaType/Tipo de papel: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 23.0 AnySetup *MediaType
*DefaultMediaType: Normal
*MediaType Standard/Papel HC (estßndar): "%PPD_MediaType=0"
*MediaType HiGrade/Papel HC mate (gran calidad): "%PPD_MediaType=1"
*MediaType Normal/Papel estßndar: "%PPD_MediaType=2"
*MediaType PCardIJ/Tarjeta postal (IJ): "%PPD_MediaType=3"
*MediaType PostCard/Tarjeta postal: "%PPD_MediaType=4"
*MediaType Normal1/estßndar 1: "%PPD_MediaType=7"
*MediaType HiQuality1/gran calidad 1: "%PPD_MediaType=8"
*MediaType HiQuality2/gran calidad 2: "%PPD_MediaType=9"
*MediaType Envelope/Sobre: "%PPD_MediaType=10"
*MediaType PastePaper/Cartulina: "%PPD_MediaType=11"
*MediaType PastePaperIJ/Cartulin-IJ: "%PPD_MediaType=12"
*?MediaType: "
  (PaperType ?\0) 16 string /CPSI /ProcSet findresource
  /externalcommand get exec pop
   dup (1) eq { pop (Standard) } {
     dup (2) eq { pop (HiGrade) } {
      dup (3) eq { pop (Normal) } {
       dup (4) eq { pop (PCardIJ) } {
        dup (5) eq { pop (PostCard) } {
         dup (8) eq { pop (Normal1) } {
          dup (9) eq { pop (HiQuality1) } {
           dup (10) eq { pop (HiQuality2) } {
            dup (11) eq { pop (Envelope) } {
             dup (12) eq { pop (PastePaper) } {
              dup (13) eq { pop (PasterPaperIJ) } {
               pop (Standard)
              } ifelse
             } ifelse
            } ifelse
           } ifelse
          } ifelse
         } ifelse
        } ifelse
       } ifelse
      } ifelse
     } ifelse
    } ifelse
  ="
*End
*CloseUI: *MediaType

*OpenUI *NTLDensity/Imprimir densidad: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 24.0 AnySetup *NTLDensity
*DefaultNTLDensity: 3
*NTLDensity 1/Densidad 1 (claro): "%PPD_Density=1"
*NTLDensity 2/Densidad 2 (ligeramente claro): "%PPD_Density=2"
*NTLDensity 3/Densidad 3 (estßndar): "%PPD_Density=3"
*NTLDensity 4/Densidad 4 (ligeramente oscuro): "%PPD_Density=4"
*NTLDensity 5/Densidad 5 (oscuro): "%PPD_Density=5"
*?NTLDensity: "
  (Density ?\0) 16 string /CPSI /ProcSet findresource
  /externalcommand get exec pop
   dup (0) eq { pop (0) } {
    dup (1) eq { pop (1) } {
     dup (2) eq { pop (2) } {
      dup (3) eq { pop (3) } {
       dup (4) eq { pop (4) } {
        dup (5) eq { pop (5) } {
         pop (0)
        } ifelse
       } ifelse
      } ifelse
     } ifelse
    } ifelse
   } ifelse
  ="
*End
*CloseUI: *NTLDensity

