*% ========== Device Setting ===========================================

*OpenUI *NTLRotation/Rotaci¾n imagen: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 28.0 AnySetup *NTLRotation
*DefaultNTLRotation: Auto
*NTLRotation Auto/Automßtica: "%PPD_Rotation=-1"
*NTLRotation 0/0 grados: "%PPD_Rotation=0"
*NTLRotation 90/90 grados: "%PPD_Rotation=1"
*NTLRotation 180/180 grados: "%PPD_Rotation=2"
*NTLRotation 270/270 grados: "%PPD_Rotation=3"
*?NTLRotation: "
  (Rotation ?\0) 16 string /CPSI /ProcSet findresource
  /externalcommand get exec pop
  dup (Auto) eq { pop (Auto) } {
  dup (0) eq { pop (0) } {
   dup (90) eq { pop (90) } {
    dup (180) eq { pop (180) } {
     dup (270) eq { pop (270) } {
        pop (Auto)
     } ifelse
    } ifelse
   } ifelse
  } ifelse
  } ifelse
  ="
*End
*CloseUI: *NTLRotation

