*OrderDependency: 199.5 PageSetup *NTLDuplex
*DefaultNTLDuplex: DuplexNoTumble
*NTLDuplex None/DESACTIVADO: "
NTLLastSetPageDevice
%PPD_Duplex=0
%PPD_end
"
*End
*NTLDuplex DuplexNoTumble/Encuadernaci¾n lado largo: "
NTLLastSetPageDevice
%PPD_Duplex=1
%PPD_end
"
*End
*NTLDuplex DuplexTumble/Encuadernaci¾n lado corto: "
NTLLastSetPageDevice
%PPD_Duplex=2
%PPD_end
"
*End
*?NTLDuplex: "
  currentpagedevice dup /Duplex get {
    /Tumble get {(DuplexTumble)} {(DuplexNoTumble)} ifelse
  }{pop (None)} ifelse =
"
*End
*CloseUI: *NTLDuplex

